wages are going to be.

01:08:36.448 --> 01:08:39.283
So anybody giving a pension
plan that's indexed to future

01:08:39.283 --> 01:08:42.420
wages would know what the market
price of those things are,

01:08:42.420 --> 01:08:44.470
so it would dramatically help
pension plans as well.

01:08:44.470 --> 01:08:49.238
Anyway, that's my idea for
Social Security.

